h1_title: The Beguiling Chant of the Pagoda Realm
content: Up ahead, watch out for an ambushing Frozen Corpse before you reach another long wooden plank that you'll need to cross. You may also run into another Lantern Sentry on this section of the walkway, so be sure to take him out as well.
